<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0c799a87-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s71b"><num value="71b">§ 71b.</num><heading> Status of completed addition</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Any building constructed under authority of <ref href="/us/usc/t20/s71a">section 71a of this title</ref> shall, upon completion, be a part of the National Gallery of Art.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id0c799a88-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/376/s2">Pub. L. 90–376, § 2</ref>, <date date="1968-07-05">July 5, 1968</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/82/286">82 Stat. 286</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id0c799a89-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id0c799a8a-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id0c799a8b-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was not enacted as part of <ref href="/us/act/1937-03-24/ch50">act Mar. 24, 1937, ch. 50</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/50/51">50 Stat. 51</ref>, which comprises this subchapter.</p>
</note>
